OL,3,CItalian mafia boss who escaped prison
OL,4,Cusing bed sheets re-captured
OL,6,FMarco Raduano, an Italian mafia boss
OL,7,Fwho has been on the run after escaping
OL,8,Ffrom a maximum security prison last
OL,9,Fyear by using bed sheets, has been
OL,10,Fcaptured in France, authorities say.
OL,12,FRaduano, who heads up the the Gargano
OL,13,FMafia in the southern Italian region
OL,14,Fof Puglia, broke out of a Sardinian
OL,15,Fprison last February.
OL,17,FHe was serving a 24-year sentence for
OL,18,Fdrug trafficking offences and, after
OL,19,Fhis escape, was listed as one of
OL,20,FEuropol's top 10 most dangerous
OL,21,Ffugitives.
