OL,6,FA multi-agency operation caught the 40-
OL,7,Fyear-old outside a luxury restaurant
OL,8,Fin Bastia, Corsica, where he was
OL,9,Fdining with a female companion.
OL,11,FRaduano's right-hand man, Gianluigi
OL,12,FTroiano, was also apprehended in a
OL,13,Fseparate sting by authorities in
OL,14,FGranada, Spain. He had been evading
OL,15,Fpolice capture since 2021, after
OL,16,Ffleeing house arrest.
