OL,6,FThe District Anti-Mafia Directorate of
OL,7,FBari ordered the joint-operation,
OL,8,Fwhich was carried out by Italy's
OL,9,FSpecial Operations Group - or ROS -
OL,10,Fand the provincial command of Foggia,
OL,11,Fin Puglia.
OL,13,FA statement from Italy's Interior
OL,14,FMinistry said the Spanish Guardia
OL,15,FCivil and the French Gendarmerie
OL,16,FNationale also co-operated in the
OL,17,Farrest.
